{
  "stem": "23942.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They made ridicule from the Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They made him into a nothing, unhuman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They made them to look, the Jewish people, like they were-- the most orthodox they picked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I want to cry when I think of it, even today, so many years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it brings tears to my eyes, when I think what they did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they went, and they burned the shul down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I saw it in flames.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Until today, I see in my mind's eye the shul burning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I see it with flames going up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I think of how [NON-ENGLISH] didn't stop the flame.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They went straight to heaven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they burned down the beis medrash, which was built from wood.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was a very tall structure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It must have stood there how many, who knows, maybe more than 100, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Who knows how long it was built.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was a very tall beis medrash.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And that's where the men learned, Gemara and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The house of study.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They burned it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Until today, there's nothing there, because I went back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And it's an empty spot, like a hole in the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "There's nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You would never believe that once there stood a beis medrash.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The shul, I was told by people, was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And it's shown in one of the paintings in the book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It was inside, I was told, it was a beautiful shul.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And it was typically built with a bimah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the men sat downstairs, all surrounding the bimah around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And the women sat upstairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I remember sitting on shabbos, going either with my grandmother or my mother to sit with all the ladies came from the town, to sit.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
